headline: Energy Toolbase and BPi Implement Energy Storage and Control System at Korbel Winery
summary: Energy Toolbase and Napa-based EPC, BPi, successfully deployed three energy storage systems (ESS) at the world-renowned Korbel Winery in California. The installation is part of the winery's broader commitment to advancing sustainability and integrating renewable energy across its operations.
